                              <width>46</width>
                           </dimensions>, on a chainline, c. 36 mm. between chainlines); also 'Krone mit zweikonturigem Bogel ohne Stern über Kreuz, ohne Beizeichen' (Piccard's type vi) (fols. 31, 33, 36, 37, height c. 145 mm., on a chainline, c. 35 mm. between chainlines); both motifs attested from the late fifteenth century. The front pastedown has a watermark 'Dreiberg mit Kreuz', <dimensions type="watermark" unit="mm">
